<p><strong></strong>Welcome to <strong>Sprint #2</strong> of <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/events/293162500/">Intro to Software Development</a></strong>.</p>
<p><strong>Scorecard</strong></p>
<p>~ Eight members signed up for Intro to Software Development<br />~ Three members made the commitment to begin<br />~ One member completed Sprint #1</p>
<p><strong>Next Steps</strong></p>
<p><strong></strong>This second sprint will last one week and will cover the second of three courses in <strong><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/learning/paths/career-essentials-in-software-development-by-microsoft-and-linkedin">Career Essentials in Software Development by Microsoft and LinkedIn</a></strong>—a LinkedIn Learning Path. Once you log into your LinkedIn account, you have <strong>FREE</strong> access to this six-hour, three-course certificate program.</p>
<p>By now you should have posted a brief update to <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53875156">Introduce Yourself</a></strong> which will acknowledge your commitment to begin this training opportunity. You may begin your journey at any time. However, the first step in starting the journey is making the commitment to begin.</p>
<p><strong>Sprint #2</strong> covers <strong><span>Programming Foundations: Fundamentals</span></strong>. This second of three sprints begins on May 22 and concludes on May 28, 2023. Once you complete this two-hour course you will receive a certificate of completion you can post to your LinkedIn profile. Please share a link to your certificate at <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53885363/">Sprint 2—Intro to Software Development</a></strong> so that I can monitor participant progress. Of course, you should start with <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53879699/">Sprint 1—Intro to Software Development</a></strong> before you move on to <strong>Sprint 2</strong>.</p>
<p>Links to all discussions are posted at <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53874249">Master Discussion List</a>.</strong></p>
<p>Let's keep developing.</p>
